Create a Slicer 11

How to create a Slicer:


x


1. Click on the slicer icon in visualizations

2. Expand "Human_Resources_Dataset", select and drag "Year" to below "Field"

3. Click on caret at the top right of box and click on "dropdown" option to change to "All"

4. Click on "Format" icon to change color, fonts size, title format, border etc.
